author: COMSOL
description:
When several components are to be electroplated they are typically mounted on a rack in the electroplating bath.

An important aspect is then achieving a uniform thickness of the plated layer for all components mounted on the rack.

This example model allows for investigating the effect of several geometrical and operational parameters on the rack electroplating uniformity.
